42:31.534 --> 42:34.768
I just couldn't stand
for you to be unhappy.

42:38.174 --> 42:39.673
(siren approaching)

42:39.675 --> 42:43.110
(tires screech, car doors open, close)

42:44.079 --> 42:47.714
OFFICER: Police! Stay
right where you are!

42:47.716 --> 42:51.118
We will use force if you do not comply.

42:52.588 --> 42:55.122
Hold it right there!

